Fri Jul 3 13:23:40 UTC 2026 - Luca Boccassi <luca.boccassi@gmail.com>

- Import version 0.10.0
  This release adds an async API for all functions that communicate
  via DBus. The API is modeled similar to gdbus. Manpages for tools
  are also now provided.

